    • Property

      public Property​(java.lang.String propertyName, java.lang.String city, double rentAmount, java.lang.String owner)
      Parameterized constructor with no info about the plot. Initializes propertyName, city, rentAmount, and owner.
      Parameters:
      propertyName - Name of the property
      city - Name of the city where the property is located
      rentAmount - How much the property costs to rent
      owner - Name of the property's owner

    • Property

      public Property​(java.lang.String propertyName, java.lang.String city, double rentAmount, java.lang.String owner, int x, int y, int width, int depth)
      Parametrized constructor with info about the plot. Initializes propertyName, city, rentAmount, owner, the coordinates for the upper left corner of the plot, as well as the width and depth of the plot.
      Parameters:
      propertyName - : Name of the property
      city - : Name of the city where property is located
      owner - : Name of the owner of the property
      rentAmount - : How much it costs to rent the property
      x - : x-value of the property's plot
      y - : y-value of the property's plot
      width - : Horizontal size of the property
      depth - : Vertical size of the property
